#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:183
msgid ""
"A raw-code element contains code, either bytecode or native machine code."
"  Its contents are:"
msgstr "原始代码元素包含代码，字节码或本地机器代码。 其内容是："

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:189
msgid "type, size and whether there are sub-raw-code elements"
msgstr "类型、大小以及是否存在子原始代码元素"

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:190
msgid "code (bytecode or machine code)"
msgstr "代码（字节码或机器代码）"

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:191
msgid "number of sub-raw-code elements (only if non-zero)"
msgstr "子原始代码元素的数量(仅当非零时)"

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:192
msgid "sub-raw-code elements"
msgstr "子原始代码元素"

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:195
msgid ""
"The first vuint in a raw-code element encodes the type of code stored in "
"this element (the two least-significant bits), whether this raw-code has "
"any children (the third least-significant bit), and the length of the "
"code that follows (the amount of RAM to allocate for it)."
msgstr ""
"原始代码元素中的第一个 vuint "
"编码存储在该元素中的代码类型（两个最低有效位），该原始代码是否有任何子代码(第三个最低有效位)，以及后面代码的长度(为其分配的RAM量)。"

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:200
msgid ""
"Following the vuint comes the code itself.  Unless the code type is viper"
" code with relocations, this code is constant data and does not need to "
"be modified."
msgstr "在vuint之后是代码本身。除非代码类型是带有重定位的viper代码，否则该代码是常量数据，不需要修改。"

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:203
msgid ""
"If this raw-code has any children (as indicated by a bit in the first "
"vuint), following the code comes a vuint counting the number of sub-raw-"
"code elements."
msgstr "如果此原始代码有任何子代码(如第一个vuint中的位所示)，则代码后面是一个vuint，用于计算子原始代码元素的数量。"

#: ../../reference/mpyfiles.rst:206
msgid "Finally any sub-raw-code elements are stored, recursively."
msgstr "最后，递归地存储所有sub-raw-code元素。"
